entries.journal_entry_description: My mission is to attack the Empire's forces from the ground up. My targets will begin with their elite forces and then on throughout their officers.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Eliminate 5 Imperial Stormtrooper Colonels in an Imperial controlled city.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Destroy 10 Elite Sandtroopers in an Imperial controlled city.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Neutralize 3 Imperial Corporals in an Imperial controlled city.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Eliminate 2 Imperial Sergeants in an Imperial controlled city.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Assassinate an Imperial Master Sergeant in an Imperial controlled city.
